{"tid":2292344,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"東京大學校花選舉2020　出爐冠軍激似石原里美、落選佳麗似進藤光","createTime":"2020-11-19T11:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T18:14:13.000Z","uid":147522,"like":7,"dislike":366,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"5a6478b0e084cb03016e6b698e5c2375a385e7a1","tid":2292344,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T11:56:02.000Z","msg":"女神石原里美在10月宣布已經與圈外男友結婚，令不少宅男粉絲夢碎。不過宅男的新希望出現了！「東京大學校花選舉2020」（ミス東大コンテスト2020）最近公布賽果，冠軍竟然與日劇女王石原里美十分相似！<br />\n<br />\n「東京大學校花選舉2020」由東京大學廣告研究會主辦，是東大一年一度的盛事。主辦方賽前為參賽者在攝影棚拍攝了宣傳硬照並上載在官網，不過硬照是最難駕馭的照片，容易將人的輪廓線條顯得生硬僵直，令各位佳麗的照片「出晒事」。<br />\n<br />\n其實看參賽者在社交網站上載的照片，大多都較自然好看，就算是用手機隨意拍的照片雖有修圖痕跡亦不至於太誇張。選舉決賽已在本月15日舉行，由5強中選出冠軍和亞軍，其他佳麗則不設排名。首先看看亞軍和落選佳麗的照片。<br />\n<br />\n而選舉的冠軍是1號神谷明采，年僅20歲，是教養學部一年級生。據日媒報導指，她其實是一個對自己沒自信的人，但在朋友推薦下才參加比賽，結果更贏得冠軍。在比賽直播頻道上，神谷明采在最尾以婚紗造型出場時，吸引不少網民湧出讚她可愛，又有網民在相關報導留言指她很似石原里美。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cH2RN1x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcH2RN1x.jpg&h=5cc0f935&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2miQ3zS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2miQ3zS.jpg&h=67f25ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xoc2UGy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxoc2UGy.jpg&h=dc10f39c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3MHis1y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3MHis1y.jpg&h=f2752d60&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GOhnaeU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGOhnaeU.jpg&h=f2dc5cb8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p05geGz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp05geGz.jpg&h=fd6004bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ka5zLOf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fka5zLOf.jpg&h=4610ca60&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Utbvi8g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUtbvi8g.jpg&h=3c9089cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b40b915cf1382c413d8b8af588c3f86ba3d1565","tid":2292344,"uid":150610,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T12:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e517d1919d623e9b7ca02353a391982cb52e5a55","tid":2292344,"uid":10125,"like":233,"dislike":6,"score":227,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T12:20:26.000Z","msg":"邊個係冠軍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n係咪冇真石原混咗係入面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5740f379e33cd426234854c7715d1e40b8d8dfb9","tid":2292344,"uid":164210,"like":318,"dislike":1,"score":317,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T12:57:01.000Z","msg":"入嚟想睇進藤光"},{"pid":"dfba66a004302ae644a47757390f41bc691de87f","tid":2292344,"uid":673,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T12:57:45.000Z","msg":"進騰光喺邊?"},{"pid":"74e954d80f45a44452e2390313ab58c789f523b3","tid":2292344,"uid":119697,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T12:58:27.000Z","msg":"都唔似我老婆"},{"pid":"3e8e55de967d0dcf06c00bbd9e6689c9687190cd","tid":2292344,"uid":22553,"like":7,"dislike":82,"score":-75,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T12:58:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HVFzL89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHVFzL89.jpg&h=c60f6066&s={SIZE}\" />真係咁似既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd6f05c11d77c3ba1b6ebb06c3a778da2abddb7","tid":2292344,"uid":38757,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T13:00:10.000Z","msg":"進藤光反而仲靚<br />\n我覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc6e6