r />\n<br />\n其實看參賽者在社交網站上載的照片，大多都較自然好看，就算是用手機隨意拍的照片雖有修圖痕跡亦不至於太誇張。選舉決賽已在本月15日舉行，由5強中選出冠軍和亞軍，其他佳麗則不設排名。首先看看亞軍和落選佳麗的照片。<br />\n<br />\n而選舉的冠軍是1號神谷明采，年僅20歲，是教養學部一年級生。據日媒報導指，她其實是一個對自己沒自信的人，但在朋友推薦下才參加比賽，結果更贏得冠軍。在比賽直播頻道上，神谷明采在最尾以婚紗造型出場時，吸引不少網民湧出讚她可愛，又有網民在相關報導留言指她很似石原里美。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cH2RN1x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcH2RN1x.jpg&h=5cc0f935&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2miQ3zS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2miQ3zS.jpg&h=67f25ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xoc2UGy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxoc2UGy.jpg&h=dc10f39c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3MHis1y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3MHis1y.jpg&h=f2752d60&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GOhnaeU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGOhnaeU.jpg&h=f2dc5cb8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p05geGz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp05geGz.jpg&h=fd6004bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ka5zLOf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fka5zLOf.jpg&h=4610ca60&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Utbvi8g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUtbvi8g.jpg&h=3c9089cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T05:38:55.000Z","msg":"早知真人版穩佢做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc1faf4f9d5aef611a08a59fb2e45ee6b4a617b","tid":2292344,"uid":290118,"like":92,"dislike":2,"score":90,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T05:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xoc2UGy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxoc2UGy.jpg&h=dc10